}
```

Also available: `PatientService` with `GetOwnersAsync()` to get list of owners.

Models:
```csharp
public enum InvoiceStatus { Pending, Paid, PartiallyPaid, Cancelled }
public enum PaymentMethod { Cash, CreditCard, DebitCard, Check, BankTransfer }
public class Invoice { int Id; int OwnerId; Owner Owner; int? AppointmentId; DateTime CreatedDate; DateTime? DueDate; InvoiceStatus Status; List<InvoiceLineItem> LineItems; List<Payment> Payments; decimal Total; decimal AmountPaid; decimal Balance; }
public class InvoiceLineItem { int Id; int InvoiceId; string Description; decimal Amount; int Quantity; }
public class Payment { int Id; int InvoiceId; Invoice Invoice; decimal Amount; PaymentMethod Method; DateTime PaidDate; string? Reference; bool IsRefunded; }
public class Owner { int Id; string FullName; string FirstName; string LastName; }
```

Create these pages (all must have `@attribute [Authorize]` and `@rendermode InteractiveServer`):

1. **Invoices.razor** (`@page "/billing"`) - List all invoices with filter by status (All, Pending, Paid, PartiallyPaid, Cancelled). Show columns: Invoice #, Owner, Date, Total, Paid, Balance, Status (with color badge). "Create Invoice" button. Click row to view details.

2. **InvoiceDetail.razor** (`@page "/billing/invoice/{Id:int}"`) - Full invoice view. Shows owner info, dates, status badge. Line items table with Description, Qty, Unit Price, Line Total. Ability to add/remove line items inline. Shows payment history for this invoice. "Record Payment" button opens inline payment form. Payment form: Amount (pre-filled with Balance), Payment Method (dropdown), Reference (text), Date. Grand total, amount paid, balance remaining prominently displayed.

3. **InvoiceForm.razor** (`@page "/billing/invoice/new"`) - Create new invoice. Select Owner (dropdown), Due Date, then add line items (Description, Amount, Quantity) dynamically with Add/Remove buttons. Show running total. On save, navigate to invoice detail.

4. **PaymentHistory.razor** (`@page "/billing/payments"`) - List all payments with columns: Date, Invoice #, Owner, Amount, Method, Reference, Refunded. Filter by owner (dropdown). Sortable by date.

Use `@using VetClinic.Data.Models`, `@using VetClinic.Services`, `@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization`, `@inject BillingService BillingService`, `@inject PatientService PatientService` (where needed), `@inject NavigationManager Navigation`.

Use Bootstrap CSS classes. Status badges should use appropriate Bootstrap colors (success=Paid, warning=Pending, info=PartiallyPaid, secondary=Cancelled).

